ht of choice shall have devolved upon them . Sections 1 and 2 shall take effect on the 15th day of October following the ratification of this article . This article shall be inoperative unless it shall have been ratified as an amendment to the Constitution by the legislatures of three - fourths of the several states within seven years from the date of its submission .	0
